msgid ""
"The SQL files are read by the :djadmin:`sqlcustom` and :djadmin:`sqlall` "
"commands in :doc:`manage.py </ref/django-admin>`. Refer to the "
":doc:`manage.py documentation </ref/django-admin>` for more information."
